'''2012–13年歐洲冠軍聯賽'''是第 58 屆[[歐洲冠軍聯賽|歐洲冠軍聯賽]]。決賽將會在[[英國|英國]][[倫敦|倫敦]]的[[溫布利球場|溫布利球場]]進行。這是[[溫布利球場|溫布利球場]]第七次舉辦歐冠決賽的賽事（舊球場和新球場合計）<ref>{{Cite web |title=Wembley chosen to host 2013 Champions League final |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/13783154.stm |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] |date=16 June 2011 |accessdate=2012-03-28 |archive-date=2012-10-04 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6BAq3UBmm?url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/13783154 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |title=Wembley Stadium to host 2013 Uefa Champions League final as FA celebrates 150th anniversary |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/competitions/champions-league/8578901/Wembley-Stadium-to-host-2013-Uefa-Champions-League-final-as-FA-celebrates-150th-anniversary.html |publisher=[[Daily_Telegraph|Daily Telegraph]] |date=16 June 2011 |accessdate=16 June 2011 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110712022524/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/competitions/champions-league/8578901/Wembley-Stadium-to-host-2013-Uefa-Champions-League-final-as-FA-celebrates-150th-anniversary.html |archivedate=2011-07-12 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

== 參賽席位 ==
本屆比賽一共有 76 支球隊，分別來自[[歐洲足球協會聯盟|歐洲足協]]的 52 個協會（不包括[[列支敦士登|列支敦士登]]）參賽，每國獲得的參賽席位數根據2011年[[歐洲足聯積分排名|歐洲足聯聯賽排名]]（UEFA league coefficient）決定，這數據是根據[[歐洲|歐洲]]各國球會於 2006–07 球季至 2010–11 球季期間，在歐洲賽的成績來定出。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.xs4all.nl/~kassiesa/bert/uefa/data/method4/crank2011.html|title=UEFA Country Ranking 2011|publisher=Bert Kassies|accessdate=2012-06-20|archive-date=2011-05-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110515233837/http://www.xs4all.nl/~kassiesa/bert/uefa/data/method4/crank2011.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

